<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<Defs>
	<AlienRace.ThingDef_AlienRace ParentName="JorisfolkRace">
		<defName>SW_Alien_AnimeMascotJoris</defName>
		<label>Anime Mascot Joris</label>
		<description>This Joris was designed by an Urbworld corporation to sell underworld products to susceptible Urbworld youths. It has become synonymous with the particular product that it was bred to try and sell and is frequently laughed at. It is often the sexual fantasy of any RimWorld dweeb who will endlessly patrol the colony's intranet trying to defend their waifu from unwarranted criticism. Or, in the case of pre-industrial colonies, draw naughty pictures of it and post them in a corkboard, probably.\n\nThe Joris Bear (Ursus Bonsonae) is a genetically modified variant of the polar and grizzly bears, adapted to life in the hostile environments of the Rim. It is thought that the original Joris Bear was created as a mockery of an obscure political figure from Old Earth's antiquity, and different variants of it were generated both by natural and artificial evolution.\n\nSpecial mechanics: Nuzzle period of 2 days. Colonists nearby will feel a deep desire for the Anime Mascot Joris, empowering them and making them feel wanted. Bonus content if you install the forbidden mod! Actually, no, I refuse to code that.</description>
        <race>
            <useMeatFrom>JE_PerfectlyNormalJoris</useMeatFrom>
        </race>
        <alienRace>
			<generalSettings>
				<alienPartGenerator>
					<aliencrowntypes>
						<li>AMJ</li>
					</aliencrowntypes>
					<alienbodytypes>
						<li>AMJ</li>
					</alienbodytypes>
				</alienPartGenerator>
			</generalSettings>
		 <graphicPaths>
			 <li>
				 <lifeStageDefs>
					<li>AdultJorisStage</li>
				 </lifeStageDefs>
			   <body>Pawn/AnimeMascotJoris/Body/</body>
			   <head>Pawn/AnimeMascotJoris/Head/</head>
                 <skeleton>Pawn/PerfectlyNormalJoris/Body/Rotten</skeleton>
                 <skull>Pawn/PerfectlyNormalJoris/Head/Skull</skull>
			   <customDrawSize>(1.7, 1.7)</customDrawSize>
			   <customPortraitDrawSize>(1.2, 1.2)</customPortraitDrawSize>
			   <customHeadDrawSize>(1.7, 1.7)</customHeadDrawSize>
			   <customPortraitHeadDrawSize>(1.2, 1.2)</customPortraitHeadDrawSize>
                    <headOffsetDirectional>
                        <north>(0, 0.79)</north>
                        <east>(1.07, 0.24)</east>
                        <south>(0, -0.08)</south>
                        <west>(-1.07, 0.24)</west>
                    </headOffsetDirectional>
			 </li>
			 <li>
			   <lifeStageDefs>
				<li>TeenJorisStage</li>
			   </lifeStageDefs>
			   <body>Pawn/AnimeMascotJoris/Body/</body>
			   <head>Pawn/AnimeMascotJoris/Head/</head>
                 <skeleton>Pawn/PerfectlyNormalJoris/Body/Rotten</skeleton>
